---
import logo from "../img/thai-sensation-logo.png";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import tick from "../img/tick-bttn.png";
import close from "../img/close-bttn.png";
---

<div
  id="ageModal"
  class="modal !hidden absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-modal z-[2000] items-center justify-center"
>
  <div
    class="modal-content text-white-main absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 w-[90%] bg-redy-400 max-w-[400px] rounded-2xl mx-auto p-4 text-center flex flex-wrap flex-col items-center"
  >
    <Image src={logo} alt="logo" width="160" height="120" loading="eager"/>
    <h2 class="my-3">Verificarea vârstei</h2>
    <p class="opacity-70 w-[90%] mb-2">
      Site-ul conține materiale destinate exclusiv persoanelor adulte și poate include
      imagini sau conținut explicit. 
    </p>
    <p class="opacity-70 w-[90%]">
      Utilizarea site-ului implică acceptarea
      acestui conținut și confirmarea vârstei de cel puțin 18 ani.
    </p>
    <h4 class="text-3xl font-medium my-4 italic">Aveți peste 18 ani?</h4>
    <div class="flex gap-4 mb-5">
      <div class="bg-white-main bttn-age text-black-main" id="yesButton">
        <Image src={tick} alt="logo" width="33" height="33" loading="eager"/>
        <p>Da</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-black-main bttn-age" id="noButton">
        <Image src={close} alt="logo" width="33" height="33" loading="eager"/>
        <p>Nu</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm opacity-80"><span>©</span>Thai Sensation 2023</p>
  </div>
</div>
